ml.clustering

Class NMF

  • java.lang.Object
    • ml.clustering.Clustering
      • ml.clustering.L1NMF
        • ml.clustering.NMF

  • public class NMF
extends L1NMF
    A Java implementation for NMF which solves the following optimization problem:

    min || X - G * F ||_F^2
    s.t. G >= 0, F >= 0

    Version:
    1.0 Jan. 31st, 2014
    Author:
    Mingjie Qian
